Fidelity Pay

A modern digital banking and fintech web application prototype inspired by the next generation of African banking platforms.

Fidelity Pay provides a secure, responsive, and user-friendly interface for managing finances, sending money, paying bills, and monitoring transactions across devices.

---

Overview

Fidelity Pay is a frontend banking dashboard designed to demonstrate modern fintech user experience principles, responsive web design, and interactive financial interfaces.

The project simulates a digital banking environment with authentication screens, account management features, transaction tracking, analytics, and security-focused design elements.

---

Features

Authentication & Security

- Secure login interface
- Password strength indicator
- Two-Factor Authentication (2FA) simulation
- Security status dashboard
- Biometric login placeholders
- Dark mode support

Account Dashboard

- Account balance display
- Balance visibility toggle
- Savings overview
- Monthly financial summaries
- Personalized user experience

Transactions

- Transaction history
- Credit and debit tracking
- Real-time transaction simulation
- Interactive transaction notifications

Payments & Transfers

- Send money
- Request payments
- Account top-up
- Bill payment simulation
- Mobile money integration concepts

Analytics

- Income and expense visualization
- Financial performance indicators
- Interactive mini-charts

Responsive Design

- Mobile-first architecture
- Tablet optimization
- Desktop dashboard layout
- Sidebar navigation
- Bottom navigation for mobile users

